TY  - JOUR
T1  - Unpacking Firm External Dependence: How Government Contract Dependence Affects Firm Investments and Market Performance
AU  - Abdurakhmonov, Mirzokhidjon
AU  - Ridge, Jason W.
AU  - Hill, Aaron D.
Y1  - 2020/01/30
PY  - 2020
DA  - 2021/02/01
N1  - doi: 10.5465/amj.2018.0067
DO  - 10.5465/amj.2018.0067
T2  - Academy of Management Journal
JF  - Academy of Management Journal
JO  - AMJ
SP  - 327
